{"tid":2012475,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[集體作文] 一人一句發展攬炒論述","createTime":"2020-05-11T15:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T17:41:43.000Z","uid":166528,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8aaa01fa7f1105da2672f5723a8175a322324c05","tid":2012475,"uid":166528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T15:56:12.000Z","msg":"聽完攬炒巴既錄音同今集城寨，我同意攬炒要有完整既論述，先至唔會被人扭曲左<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁你想點？</span></span><br />\n我文筆唔好，所以需要同大家集思廣益，發展一套完整論述出黎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點做？</span></span><br />\n我會係下面既每一層提出一個問題<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">假設我係＃３寫</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">乜野係攬炒？</span></strong><br />\n</span><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果你對呢個問題有想法</span></span><br />\n1. 引用＃３<br />\n2. 寫低你既論點，一句起兩句止都唔怕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">假設你係＃１５寫</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">攬炒係一個過程</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果你想補充或者挑戰呢個論點</span></span><br />\n引用＃１５<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果你想提出新論點</span></span><br />\n引用＃３<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果想推POST或其他話題</span></span><br />\n用普通回覆<br />\n<br />\n到每條問題累積到咁上下既引用我就會將同一條問題既所有論點歸納，嘗試整理出一段論述出黎，最後整篇文章會做置頂或者另開一個POST。"},{"pid":"a6c5c209bb250a22883bd7f3c54a6a289baac768","tid":2012475,"uid":166528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T15:56:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">乜野係攬炒？</span>"},{"pid":"ad009641df487248750bf49b092c8f8cd1977a59","tid":2012475,"uid":166528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T15:57:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點解要攬炒？</span>"},{"pid":"eca61c2e20ed24458ddec1fd99b44731798da6ee","tid":2012475,"uid":166528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6c5c209bb250a22883bd7f3c54a6a289baac768","tid":2012475,"uid":166528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T15:56:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">乜野係攬炒？</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T15:57:44.000Z","msg":"攬炒唔係Burnism,係Phoenixism，係鳳凰重生既必經過程。（攬炒巴講得太好，所以要引用佢）"},{"pid":"bc8dd1272b77b99c2704d429a64171ca0c028e0d","tid":2012475,"uid":166528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6c5c209bb250a22883bd7f3c54a6a289baac768","tid":2012475,"uid":166528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T15:56:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">乜野係攬炒？</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T15:58:10.000Z","msg":"攬炒係先破後立既前置工作，為日後香港重光鋪路"},{"pid":"4972315859d32858307f9c8d144c1910945ccab5","tid":2012475,"uid":166528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad009641df487248750bf49b092c8f8cd1977a59","tid":2012475,"uid":166528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T15:57:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點解要攬炒？</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T15:58:30.000Z","msg":"香港長久以黎被政治經濟結構被中共侵蝕，長久下去必定榨乾香港優勢"},{"pid":"27d15fdc720a1d9ab5d45e090dcb3058a164396b","tid":2012475,"uid":166528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad009641df487248750bf49b092c8f8cd1977a59","tid":2012475,"uid":166528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T15:57:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點解要攬炒？</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T15:58:45.000Z","msg":"只有靠攬炒先能夠將中共既勢力趕走，重建屬於香港人既環境"},{"pid":"a756f9ffb35d380307764d6bf18773c407145f68","tid":2012475,"uid":166528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T16:00:29.000Z","msg":"暫時淨係諗到咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨番既靠大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/no